{% comment %}
  Name: sections/mar26-catalog-engine.liquid
  Version: 2.4.1 (Catalogv Card Variation)
  Description: Groups products by Category Banner blocks and provides anchor navigation.
  Changelog:
    - 2.4.1: Supported 5-row height locked alignment.
    - 2.4.0: Added selected_products block setting of type product_list to enable customizer-driven manual product listings and overlaps.
    - 2.3.2: Implemented client-side ResizeObserver fallback rows logic.
    - 2.3.1: Isolated 2-column mobile layout for catalogv card.
    - 2.3.0: Added catalogv card variation toggle and dynamic snippet routing.
{% endcomment %}

<style>
